{"tid":1276654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最近打AOC 嘅新兵種、撳咗嘅升級制","createTime":"2019-07-02T04:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T04:12:23.000Z","uid":267969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"78d39ecd28b4ea6c98cb407975d21579e2f7cb0a","tid":1276654,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"<strong>化學</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.aoetw.com/_nuxt/img/79a6bda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aoetw.com%2F_nuxt%2Fimg%2F79a6bda.jpg&h=ea6a6a72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>輕型衝撞車</strong><br />\n輕型衝撞車是世紀帝國II遊戲中，沒有人駕駛卻可以講話的神奇軍事單位，它可以從攻城器製造所製造，對一般單位的攻擊力較低，對建築物、攻城器單位皆有額外的傷害加成<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.aoetw.com/_nuxt/img/1bc32fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aoetw.com%2F_nuxt%2Fimg%2F1bc32fa.jpg&h=f6653505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>僧侶</strong><br />\n僧侶是遊戲中的一個特殊單位，可以在修道院進行訓練。雖然缺乏一切攻擊手段，他們仍然佔有一席之地，因為他們是能夠將其他單位轉換為玩家己方單位（另一個是傳教士）的唯二單位之一。 <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.aoetw.com/_nuxt/img/b8983d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aoetw.com%2F_nuxt%2Fimg%2Fb8983d2.jpg&h=712a08a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n期餘嘅城牆呀、護甲呀，係2014年科技<br />\n投石手係2016年兵種<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.aoetw.com/_nuxt/img/9852346.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aoetw.com%2F_nuxt%2Fimg%2F9852346.png&h=7539aa47&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}